lead_paragraph: The Arab region squandered the chance to help elect their first FIFA president because their two candidates failed to cooperate, leaving the door open for Swiss Gianni Infantino to triumph on Friday, Arab soccer chiefs and pundits said.

headline.print_headline: Arabs Lament Missed Opportunity in FIFA Presidency Race
headline.main: Arabs Lament Missed Opportunity in FIFA Presidency Race
